[{"title":"LeetCode 1824. Minimum Sideway Jumps","url":"/2021/04/28/LeetCode-1824-Minimum-Sideway-Jumps/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-1824-Minimum-Sideway-Jumps\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-1824-Minimum-Sideway-Jumps\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 1824. Minimum Sideway Jumps\"></a>LeetCode 1824. Minimum Sideway Jumps</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/minimum-sideway-jumps/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/minimum-sideway-jumps/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<p>這題首先要定義好dp[i][j]，在此我定義為老套路<br>dp[i][j]: minimum sideway jumps to point j at lane i</p>\n<p>之後推出狀態轉移方程:<br>if obstacles[j] == i + 1 then dp[i][j] = INT_MAX(如果當前路上有障礙則無法到達)<br>else dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j] (從上一個point直接過來)</p>\n<p>注意如果只寫到這邊的話，障礙後面的dp值會被設為INT_MAX，然而這是錯誤的，因為那個點的值有可能可以被該point的其他lane更新(從同個點的不同lane跳過來)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">minSideJumps</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; obstacles)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n = obstacles.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>() - <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        vector&lt;vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&gt; <span class=\"built_in\">dp</span>(<span class=\"number\">3</span>, vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;(n+<span class=\"number\">1</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[<span class=\"number\">0</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[<span class=\"number\">1</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[<span class=\"number\">2</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; j &lt; n + <span class=\"number\">1</span>; j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> o = obstacles[j];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> cur_min = INT_MAX;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(i + <span class=\"number\">1</span> == o)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    dp[i][j] = INT_MAX;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    dp[i][j] = dp[i][j<span class=\"number\">-1</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur_min = <span class=\"built_in\">min</span>(cur_min, dp[i][j]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> k = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; k &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; k++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(k + <span class=\"number\">1</span> != o &amp;&amp; dp[k][j] &gt; cur_min)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    dp[k][j] = cur_min + <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> ans = INT_MAX;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ans = <span class=\"built_in\">min</span>(ans, dp[i][n]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["dynamic programming"]},{"title":"LeetCode 1834. Single-Threaded CPU","url":"/2021/04/25/LeetCode-1834-Single-Threaded-CPU/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-1834-Single-Threaded-CPU\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-1834-Single-Threaded-CPU\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 1834. Single-Threaded CPU\"></a>LeetCode 1834. Single-Threaded CPU</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/single-threaded-cpu/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/single-threaded-cpu/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>priority_queue(min heap)宣告方式<span id=\"more\"></span></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>根據題意我們需要照enqueue time大小依序執行task，這裡我們很自然地會希望任務以enqueue time的時間有小到大排序，但因為返回的結果是task原本的index，所以需要前處理不然順序會亂掉。</p>\n<p>在這裡因為任務處理的順序已經固定了，所以在最外面的while循環(確認ans是否已將task都處理了)裡面，會先決定以當前的時間有哪些task能加入到avalible tasks(priority_queue)裡。</p>\n<p>最後的部分則是一次處理一個task，如果avalible tasks裡面沒有task了，則cur_time變成當前idx指向的task的起始時間。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> ll;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> pair&lt;ll, ll&gt; pll;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">getOrder</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; tasks)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        priority_queue&lt;pll, vector&lt;pll&gt;, greater&lt;pll&gt;&gt; pq;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n = tasks.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; tasks.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            tasks[i].<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">sort</span>(tasks.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(), tasks.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>());</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ll cur_time = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, idx = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(ans.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>() != n)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(idx &lt; n &amp;&amp; tasks[idx][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] &lt;= cur_time)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                pq.<span class=\"built_in\">push</span>(&#123;tasks[idx][<span class=\"number\">1</span>], tasks[idx][<span class=\"number\">2</span>]&#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                idx++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(pq.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">auto</span> cur_task = pq.<span class=\"built_in\">top</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                pq.<span class=\"built_in\">pop</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                ans.<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(cur_task.second);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur_time += cur_task.first;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur_time = tasks[idx][<span class=\"number\">0</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["heap"]},{"title":"LeetCode 1838. Frequency of the Most Frequent Element","url":"/2021/04/27/LeetCode-1838-Frequency-of-the-Most-Frequent-Element/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-1838-Frequency-of-the-Most-Frequent-Element\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-1838-Frequency-of-the-Most-Frequent-Element\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 1838. Frequency of the Most Frequent Element\"></a>LeetCode 1838. Frequency of the Most Frequent Element</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/frequency-of-the-most-frequent-element/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/frequency-of-the-most-frequent-element/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<p>這題的關鍵點在於如何快速地判斷全部的元素(區間內)變為x所需要的cost是否大於k。知道這點後，透過前處理(prefix sum和sort)，就能使用sliding window的技巧解題了。</p>\n<p>可惜比賽的時候就是想不到阿，sliding window的題目要回去多做做了…</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> ll;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">maxFrequency</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">sort</span>(nums.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(), nums.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>());</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ll j = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, sum = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, ans = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            sum += nums[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 當[j, i]的元素都變成nums[i]所需的cost大於k的時候，左側窗口縮小。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(nums[i] * (i - j + <span class=\"number\">1</span>) - sum &gt; k)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                sum -= nums[j];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                j++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ans = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(ans, i - j + <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["sliding window"]},{"title":"hexo common commands","url":"/2021/04/24/hexo-common-commands/","content":"<h3 id=\"Common-Deploy-command\"><a href=\"#Common-Deploy-command\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Common Deploy command\"></a>Common Deploy command</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>","categories":["hexo"],"tags":["hexo"]}]